<idea-plugin>
    <id>org.videobug.videobug</id>
    <name>Unlogged</name>
    <vendor email="support@bug.video" url="https://unlogged.io">Unlogged</vendor>

    <idea-version since-build="221.5080.210"/>

    <description>
        <![CDATA[
            The ultimate tool for Java developers who want to speed up their testing workflow. <br />
            With Unlogged automated test case generator, you can instantly generate JUnit and Mockito test case boilerplate for any method in your codebase. <br />

            <ul>
            <li>Generate test case boilerplate instantly as you navigate to a method</li>
            <li>Mock method calls in test cases <pre>when(some.Method()).then(answer))</pre></li>
            <li>Support @Mock/@MockExtension for Mockito</li>
            <li>JUnit4 and JUnit 5 flavours</li>
            </ul>

            Simply open the Unlogged plugin and navigate to the method you want to test in your editor.
            Then, with just a few clicks, Unlogged test generator will create a complete test case for you,
            including all necessary imports, annotations, and method stubs. <br /> <br />

            But that's not all. Save the test case with one click and easily navigate to the generated test case
             and start writing your test code right away.
            No more wasting time setting up your testing environment - Unlogged test generator does it all for you.  <br /> <br />

            Download Unlogged today and start writing better tests in less time.  <br />
        ]]>
    </description>

